    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Silence</strong> (Level 2 Illusion)</p><p>For the duration, no sound can be created within or pass through a 20-foot-radius sphere centered on a point you choose within range. Any creature or object entirely inside the sphere is immune to thunder damage, and creatures are deafened while entirely inside it.</p><p>Casting a spell that includes a verbal component is impossible there.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> 120 feet | <strong>Duration:</strong> Up to 10 minutes (Concentration) (Ritual)</p><p><em>Classes: Bard, Cleric, Ranger</em></p>",
